{"tid":1668605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁蒙面法】小組主席黃定光有份捐52萬俾【的士狂徒】","createTime":"2019-10-22T05:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T05:37:41.000Z","uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"770cf4ef1ad1f12a5978defe374f539bebeede04","tid":1668605,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"政府本月5日以「先訂立、後審議」方式實施《禁止蒙面規例》，立法會《禁止蒙面規例》小組委員會今日召開首次會議，民建聯黃定光及新民黨容海恩各以 29 票當選小組委員會正副主席！<br />\n<br />\n有份捐52萬既「守護香港大聯盟」頭幾個總會就係黃定光既組織<br />\n黃定光現擔任職位：香港中華出入口商會副會長，香港中華總商會選任會董，港九百貨業商會理事，香港鞋業總會榮譽會長，香港青年聯會顧問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qa6eNd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQa6eNd8.jpg&h=319c9b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ciAWf7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FciAWf7L.jpg&h=3ebcf32a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsafeguardhongkong.hk%2Finfo%2Fabout-us&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSIpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=ee89b837\" target=\"_blank\">https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us</a>"}]}